            ],
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "Bolan compels plant-based materials within 10 feet of him to grow sharp thorns and spiky branches. This ability affects all walls, floors, and large objects made from dead organic material, such as wood. Affected areas become difficult terrain. Non-fey and non-plant creatures in the affected area or those who move through an affected square take 2d10 piercing damage (DC 18 basic Reflex save). This ability does not affect stone, dirt, living plants, or other materials. The effect ends when Bolan moves out of his square.",
